descriptionMarkdown:
99% uptime completely own powered. no need to connect to any power lines.
remove snap to grid if you don't want it.

one radar needs 7 hours 20 minutes to fully reveal max area.

four of these blueprints rotated and placed in same chunk will fully reveal in 2 hours.
active view: 7x7 chunks
full view: 29x29 chunks. or 14 in each direction not counting the chunk the radar is in.

if you fill inventory with 2 stacks of solar and 2 stacks of accumulators and one stack of everything else you will be able to place 12 of them. So go into a car and drive around your base far out and and place them completely non connected to anything.

number of radars; Full reveal time:
1; 440min ~ 8h
2; 220min ~ 4h
3; 147min ~ 3h
4; 110min ~ 2h
8; 55 min  ~ 1h
12; 37 min
title: self sufficient Radar Outpost
